---
import docs from "../../data/docs.json";
import site from "../../data/site.json";
---

<section id="menubar">
  <h2>Menu bar &amp; updates</h2>
  <p>Junction has no windows and no Dock icon. Click the menu-bar icon for:</p>
  <ul>
    {docs.menubarActions.map((action) => (
      <li><b>{action.label}</b> — <Fragment set:html={action.body} /></li>
    ))}
  </ul>
  <p>Updates arrive through <a href={site.sparkle}>Sparkle</a>, and you can trigger a check from the menu bar or <b>Settings → General → Updates</b>. They're EdDSA-signed, so the app only installs builds signed with the maintainer's key. Homebrew users can also <code>brew upgrade</code> — each release bumps the cask.</p>
</section>
